{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 318207, "create_time": 1659073108, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "比方说有个邻居，是私营企业主，自己瞎投资煤矿亏损了几千万，把所有家产都搭进去了。然后他就从亲戚、邻居那疯狂借钱，许诺年利息12％，大家都觉得他公司经营得不错，就基本都会借给他。没想到他们借到钱就拿去还债，而且还买了一套房留给儿子，之后就跑路去外地了。\n我家也借了他十多万，而且那么多年也都没有还。父母打听到了他们身处何处，却又不去起诉他们。\n他们说为了十万多就把邻居告上法庭，旁人会觉得他们冷酷绝情。我完全无法理解他们的脑回路。别人借钱拿不回本息，都是直接起诉，甚至直接人肉开盒、通讯地理定位的", "timestamp": 1659073108}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 318244, "create_time": 1659074591, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 当你家没钱时自然而且必须追债。当你家有钱时，何必呢。", "timestamp": 1659074591}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 318245, "create_time": 1659074626, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 人情温暖比钱更重要。你以为你没有落难的一天？", "timestamp": 1659074626}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 318346, "create_time": 1659080650, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "羡慕富裕地区🥺", "timestamp": 1659080650}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 318504, "create_time": 1659085009, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: ？落难就可以借钱不还？", "timestamp": 1659085009}], "create_time": 1659072769, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1659085009, "likenum": 5, "n_attentions": 5, "n_comments": 5, "pid": 90283, "poll": null, "reply": 5, "text": "我发现父母那辈人顾及很多事情，不会有那种一定要通过法律手段维护自己合法权益的意识", "timestamp": 1659072769}}